api_producer_driver-redis requires the following:

* PHP (tested with 5.4)
  * phpredis (https://github.com/nicolasff/phpredis)
* Redis (tested with 2.6)
* A webserver (tested with Apache 2.2)
* api_producer (https://github.com/kimor79/api_producer)

Copy the files in php/ to <php include path>/api_producer/. E.g.:
  cp -R php /usr/local/include/php/api_producer
